{
  "stem": "25381.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The minute I said, what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Your-- your father's Israel Kukes?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I say, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He's my father.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he-- oh, my gosh!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That's your father?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Are you sure?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He has a brother in Detroit, and he's a millionaire, a Louis Kukes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIDE CONVERSATION] And he has a brother in Detroit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he-- your father had a sister in Boston.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the kids, the children-- two boys and a-- two sons and a daughter-- they live in New York.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you're telling me you-- he was so famous, my father, that he was known here, in United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, we remember your father very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Listen to that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody-- and they called right away, over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the two sons, my cousins, like first cousins-- tall, handsome, good-looking, professionals-- and the sister, they came over to the HIAS to see us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they wanted to take us in downtown, and they wanted to buy us clothes, and take us in a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, I don't need anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't want anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just wanted to, somehow, to go out from this HIAS.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'm not asking for anything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they-- the other people-- envied me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oy-- I came in a [NON-ENGLISH]-- how do you say, in English?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH]-- like I came in milk and honey.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I fall into such a good hands.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They called right away to Detroit, to my uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said to put us on the train, and to bring us right there, to Detroit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they-- they were afraid, because what's when-- who is he-- what is he?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So anyways, he promised the-- the organization, the HIAS, the director that he's-- it's true.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's a brother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he's going to take care of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fine, they put us on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
